			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				From our advertising folks: <br>  <br> You've probably noticed the big new ad on the right. We know it makes the <br> page narrower, but it is important for us to put these ads here. It takes a <br> lot of people and a lot of resources to make the VNBoards such a great <br> environment for users to interact with each other. We support tools like the <br> VNBoards by selling ads. Without ads on VNBoards, there wouldn't be any <br> VNBoards. <br>  <br> We know you probably don't like this addition to our pages, but if you like <br> the Vault sites and you like using the VNBoards, support us, and support our <br> advertisers. We want your user experience to be the best on the Web, but we <br> still have to pay our bills! Try to keep this in mind when you see an ad on <br> the boards and help keep us in business by clicking on one now and then! <br>  <br> If you want to send feedback about the ads to someone here, send your email <br> to newads@snowball.com. We do listen to your feedback! <br>  <br> Thanks for reading. <br> 
